---
title: Ghoulish Goulash Style Beef Pasta with Monster Garlic Bread
description: Family feasts don't get much creepier than this Ghoulish Goulash Style Beef Pasta. Packed with delicious ingredients and served with a scary good side of Monster Garlic Bread, spooky season just got frightfully tasty.
